metadata.name: Endless Dream
metadata.description: This black and white film image transmit me the same feeling of a dream, when you are trying to run but you can't. That situation you can get out just waking up. This NFTs will allow you to get a free copy of my next photobook, Memories Before the Dark. My first Hardcover book on a long therm project I'm working on. Documenting an ordinary American lifestyle through an European eye.
